jako B2B, co umo\u017cliwi uzyskanie zni\u017cek na op\u0142aty za sprzeda\u017c.<\/li>\n<li><b>Monitoruj i dostosowuj<\/b>: Po przes\u0142aniu, \u015bled\u017a sprzeda\u017c i w razie potrzeby dostosuj oferty, aby zoptymalizowa\u0107 wyniki.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, korzystanie z programu Bulk Services na Amazonie to skuteczny spos\u00f3b na obni\u017cenie koszt\u00f3w i zwi\u0119kszenie wolumenu sprzeda\u017cy. Je\u015bli sprzedajesz produkty B2B, to rozwi\u0105zanie zdecydowanie warto rozwa\u017cy\u0107.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Czy korzystasz z potencja\u0142u programu Bulk Services na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>W sprzeda\u017cy internetowej, <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7100,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7099","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7099"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7099"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7099\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7100"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7099"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7099"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embe